T). As the novel genus and species cannot be clearly assigned to an established family within the order Solirubrobacterales, the novel family Parviterribacteraceae fam. nov. is proposed. Emended descriptions of the classes Thermoleophilia and Rubrobacteria and their orders and families are also provided.},
